detaileddescription.para:
The two first parameters must be /path/to/data/ and /path/to/output/ Example 1 :  Faster2Root("/path/to/data /path/to/output -i index_129.id -c calib.calib -e 200 -m 4 -t timeshifts.dT ")
 Example 2 :

We want to create a DSSD trigger : int main(int argc, argv** argv)
{
  Faster2Root convertor(argc, argv, [](const Event& event)
  {
    for (int hit = 0; hit<event.mult; hit++)
    {
      if (isDSSD[event.labels[hit]]) return true;
    }
    return false;
  });
}
 Then compile the code and call : ./executable /path/to/data /path/to/output -i index_129.id -c calib.calib -e 200 -m 4 -t timeshifts.dT
